    "If you are rather indecisive, you will balance arguments for and against and possibly change your mind towards the right.",
    "A parallel argument can apply to the decision to vote or abstain.",
    "If you had already decided to abstain, you might find additional reasons to do so.",
    "If you are rather indecisive, you might weigh arguments for and against abstaining or for mobilising yourself further.",
    "In any case, it appears that the capacity for critical thinking is enhanced rather than undermined, and that autonomy is therefore preserved."
